OL,3,CCoroner calls for better water safety
OL,4,Ceducation after beach drownings
OL,6,FA coroner has written to the Education
OL,7,FSecretary calling for better water
OL,8,Fsafety for children following the
OL,9,Finquest into the deaths of two
OL,10,Fyoungsters at Bournemouth.
OL,12,FJoe Abbess, 17, from Southampton, and
OL,13,FSunnah Khan, 12, from High Wycombe,
OL,14,FBuckinghamshire, drowned and eight
OL,15,Fother people were treated by
OL,16,Fparamedics after they were thought to
OL,17,Fhave been caught in a rip current next
OL,18,Fto the pier at the Dorset seaside
OL,19,Fresort on May 31 last year.
