OL,3,CCoroner calls for better water safety
OL,4,Ceducation after beach drownings
OL,6,FHowever, Ms Griffin said that she
OL,7,Fwould be writing to Education
OL,8,FSecretary Bridget Phillipson in a
OL,9,Fprevention of future deaths report
OL,10,Fover her concerns of the lack of
OL,11,Fmandatory education in schools
OL,12,Fregarding water safety.
OL,14,FThe move was welcomed at the inquest
OL,15,Fconclusion by Vanessa Abbess, who
OL,16,Fsaid: "We feel much more can be done
OL,17,Fto improve education around water
OL,18,Fsafety.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/10
