OL,3,CCoroner calls for better water safety
OL,4,Ceducation after beach drownings
OL,6,F"We share the senior coroner's concern
OL,7,Fthat there should be mandatory water
OL,8,Fsafety education for children.
OL,10,F"Like the senior coroner, I am
OL,11,Fconcerned that this should be
OL,12,Funiversal for all children.
OL,14,F"If any message can be taken from our
OL,15,Floss, it is that rip currents can be
OL,16,Fdangerous, and everyone should know
OL,17,Fand practise the RNLI's advice of
OL,18,Ffloat to live."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/10
