OL,3,CCoroner calls for better water safety
OL,4,Ceducation after beach drownings
OL,6,FIn her report published on Friday, Ms
OL,7,FGriffin raised her concern that as of
OL,8,FMarch 2020, one in four children did
OL,9,Fnot have access to swimming lessons,
OL,10,Fwith that figure thought to have
OL,11,Fdecreased since the Covid-19 pandemic.
OL,13,FShe pointed out that the primary
OL,14,Fschool curriculum requires children to
OL,15,Fbe able to swim at least 25 metres and
OL,16,Fhave an understanding of self-rescue
OL,17,Fand survival skills.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/10
