OL,3,CCoroner calls for better water safety
OL,4,Ceducation after beach drownings
OL,6,FMs Griffin wrote: "If children do not
OL,7,Fget access to this vital lifesaving
OL,8,Feducation in school, there are
OL,9,Fconcerns as to where this awareness
OL,10,Fwill come from.
OL,12,F"Some will receive it from privately
OL,13,Ffunded swimming lessons, however, not
OL,14,Fevery child is fortunate enough to
OL,15,Fhave such lessons.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/10
