OL,3,CCoroner calls for better water safety
OL,4,Ceducation after beach drownings
OL,6,F"The Royal Lifeguarding Safety Society
OL,7,F(RLSS) and Sunnah and Joe's mothers
OL,8,Fhave been advocating for water safety
OL,9,Fto become part of the classroom part
OL,10,Fof the curriculum as opposed to the
OL,11,Fphysical education part of the
OL,12,Fcurriculum on the basis that if
OL,13,Fchildren cannot do the practical part
OL,14,Fof water safety, they will at least
OL,15,Fhave access to water safety awareness
OL,16,Fand lifesaving skills in a classroom
OL,17,Fsetting."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/10
