OL,3,CCoroner calls for better water safety
OL,4,Ceducation after beach drownings
OL,6,FShe added: "There are inherent dangers
OL,7,Fof using any form of water and it is
OL,8,Fcrucial for people to have an
OL,9,Fawareness of these risks and how to
OL,10,Fmanage them as the lack of awareness
OL,11,Fcould lead to more deaths from
OL,12,Fdrowning.
OL,14,F"An ideal opportunity to warn and
OL,15,Finform all members of the public would
OL,16,Fbe through educating children of the
OL,17,Frisks.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/10
