OL,3,CCoroner calls for better water safety
OL,4,Ceducation after beach drownings
OL,6,F"The lack of providing education to
OL,7,Fchildren around these risks through
OL,8,Fthe national classroom curriculum
OL,9,Fcould lead to future deaths."
OL,11,FShe added in the report sent to
OL,12,FBridget Phillipson: "In my opinion
OL,13,Furgent action should be taken to
OL,14,Fprevent future deaths and I believe
OL,15,Fyou and/or your organisation have the
OL,16,Fpower to take such action."
OL,18,FThe Education Secretary has a duty to
OL,19,Frespond to the coroner's report within
OL,20,F56 days.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/10
